import React from 'react'

import Helmet from '../components/Helmet/Helmet.js'
import { Container, Row, Col } from 'reactstrap'

const Home = () => {
    return (
        <Helmet title="Home">
            <section>
                <Container>
                    <Row>
                        <Col lg='6' md='6'></Col>
                    </Row>
                </Container>
            </section>
        </Helmet>
    )
}

export default Home
